snippet.title: DoDonPachi DaiOuJou (Black Label) 1st loop 1cc
snippet.description:
This run has been 4 months in the making. I have spent the past two weeks doing attempts at this run for 3-4 hours a day. Had some heartbreaking moments, but I finally got the run. I ended up playing out of my mind (at least by my standards) earlier today.

Sorry for the bad video quality, I was getting stuttering unless I dropped OBS to low settings. Also, any graphic glitches you see are a result of Shmupmame's useful, though buggy, lag reduction features.

Also, you should check out my podcast dedicated to shmups:

https://soundcloud.com/user-306325657
